# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) for `npx wrangler pages dev out/`.
# In production these are set in the Cloudflare Pages dashboard instead.

# Google Places API (for the reviews function) — restricted key + the business Place ID
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=""
PLACE_ID=""

# Web3Forms access key (contact form delivery to the owner's Gmail)
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=""

# Cloudflare Turnstile secret — ONLY needed if the optional contact-form
# hardening (functions/api/contact.ts) is enabled.
TURNSTILE_SECRET=""
